 MVVM Architecture	Clear separation of Model, View, and ViewModel
 Pull-to-Refresh	Users can pull down to reload feed using Combine triggers
 Infinite Scrolling	Automatically loads more content when reaching bottom of feed
 Modular Feed UI	Supports multiple feed types (text, image, video preview)
 Reactive Updates	Live data updates with Combine
 Pluggable Cell System	Easy to extend with new feed item types
 Dynamic Height	Content-aware cell resizing for flexible layouts
